{"tid":137383,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"最近番睇哈利波特，發現其實好多bug位","createTime":"2017-02-27T18:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T09:38:51.000Z","uid":31173,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a95fe9e02157866eaaf6d9d229408877877bc24","tid":137383,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T18:32:02.000Z","msg":"最近睇番2，3集，發現幾多bug位<br />\n<br />\n好似佢有件隱形斗篷，其實佢帶住佢做乜都已經ok，好似佢有幕夜晚蛇出去搵個逃犯，佢著住件野已經唔會俾石內卜發現<br />\n<br />\n又有幕講佢地對住個箱，只要佢地諗住佢地驚既野，個樣野打開個箱就會彈出黎，如果我最驚係條女，咁咪會彈條女出黎俾我搞？？<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他諗到再講"},{"pid":"6befda58e40823ef1fb707320e7f4b8974bed436","tid":137383,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T20:28:04.000Z","msg":"呢啲算bug咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ac37be9b6213604f050802168cb1517742e0e6","tid":137383,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"係愛呀哈利"},{"pid":"6dd0773fd017411c0161f796af2be818767da18a","tid":137383,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係愛呀哈利</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5de79bb57b764550d4c69e74e11a71b4902232","tid":137383,"uid":86727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"隱形斗篷是三大聖物之一，也是唯一一樣可以躲過死神既聖物，原本就應該BUG<br />\n而嗰個箱，如果你有依個諗法，個箱係唔會出到女畀你搞<br />\n仲要即使出到女畀你搞，佢原本應該都係百變怪<br />\n係嗰個咁既魔法世界，不如用愛情藥好過"},{"pid":"711f316da487af79a51640ecdde2146f97031a71","tid":137383,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T04:02:32.000Z","msg":"純粹唔明佢既世界觀入面<br />\n點分強弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n照道理 學咒語 求期背撚曬咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />